## OptionalKeys type

Gets keys of an object which are optional

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type OptionalKeys<T> = {
  [K in keyof T]-?: undefined extends {
    [K2 in keyof T]: K2;
  }[K]
    ? K
    : never;
}[keyof T];
```
